headline: GE Aerospace: received an order for 210 engines in Poland
summary: GE Aerospace has received an order for 210 T700 engines to power the Polish Armed Forces' 96 Boeing AH-64E Apache Guardian helicopters.The engine order follows a cooperation agreement signed in August...
